    The processor class for handling the mybatis:bind tag.
    This processor register an any value to the MyBatisâ€™s bind variables (similar to that of the <bind> provided by MyBatis core module) This class's implementation was inspired with the StandardWithTagProcessor provide by Thymeleaf.
